  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      1. To compare the efficacy of

        1. Short Daily Hemodialysis

        2. Online HDF in term of adequacy of dialysis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The investigators intend to compare the efficacy between these modalities of treatment in
      terms of adequacy and also other parameters such as calcium-phosphorus balance and hematocrit
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
